.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\">5.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 29\">Chapter 29</a>, The Reaver.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Osbert_Serry\" title=\"Osbert Serry\">Osbert Serry</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Southshield\" title=\"Lord of Southshield\">Lord of Southshield</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>&#160;– Present\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Incumbent</b>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403173032\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.117 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.344 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1851/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 13676/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 12284/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2307/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4297/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.210/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.41 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  328.916      1 -total\n 83.62%  275.039      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 83.27%  273.890      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.96%   36.047     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  7.52%   24